{"tid":2345952,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"消息︰深圳警方今早11時移交兩未成年被捕人予香港　香港警方︰中午天水圍警署交代接收兩疑犯","createTime":"2020-12-30T02:41:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-30T04:53:38.000Z","uid":20933,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"62a4856f50eec96174e2f8c9ce03cc3c2beea26e","tid":2345952,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T02:41:58.000Z","msg":"12港人涉嫌偷渡案前日（28日）在深圳市鹽田區人民法院審理。本報致電法院查詢，職員證實該案會在今早（30日）10時半宣判，公眾可以旁聽，但旁聽席已滿。被問到被告會否親自上庭，職員表示不清楚。本報查閱鹽田法院官方網頁，「開庭公告」未有顯示12港人案。<br />\n<br />\n消息稱，深圳警方將於上午約11時，在深圳灣口岸移交兩名未成年被捕人給香港警方，兩人將會先被帶到天水圍警署，其後送往檢疫。<br />\n<br />\n香港警方表示，將於中午12時在天水圍警署交代接收由內地執法機關送回兩名疑犯的事宜。<br />\n<br />\n被捕的12人中兩名未成年人廖子文及黃臨福未被起訴，檢察院早前稱會舉行不公開聽證。本報向法院職員查詢聽證日期，職員稱不清楚。<br />\n<br />\n12港人涉嫌偷渡案前日審理，據報《文匯報》及《深圳特區報》當晚報道，被告10人當庭認罪，希望法庭從輕處罰。被起訴10人中，鄧棨然、喬映瑜被控組織他人偷越邊境，鄭子豪、嚴文謙、張銘裕、張俊富、黃偉然、李子賢、李宇軒、郭子麟等8人被控偷越邊境。"},{"pid":"e0ea108b51b3a1b31623c865b336c3b5b0fc64bb","tid":2345952,"uid":127929,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T02:54:43.000Z","msg":"黑警水平仲cheap過公安<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/discover.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />九成九即坐"},{"pid":"78ee1f5fcae1bbf809a8184c38c3ff7dfe6d064f","tid":2345952,"uid":231089,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T02:56:35.000Z","msg":"Push<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />終於平安"},{"pid":"dce5e09528e24af0f11d7331fa08d2977ffe1b1b","tid":2345952,"uid":284432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T03:09:23.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"93c67849f21775c2babbe8206107134058e32014","tid":2345952,"uid":33556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T03:09:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5044199fc0f5807fdc273c6ab430b8769994aa6f","tid":2345952,"uid":214502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T03:12:33.000Z","msg":"根據香港仆街政府 送佢番黎再告過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c7ab5cffc7405896f748f776e01b43cc7cfb225","tid":2345952,"uid":127425,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T04:15:32.000Z","msg":"大陸法治好過香港"},{"pid":"f2c2f917f27979e467d2c5b0a41d56792d77691f","tid":2345952,"uid":291750,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T04:45:42.000Z","msg":"自己煮麵"},{"pid":"b698a1a498371c6478045907057de0590dd62a09","tid":2345952,"uid":291750,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T04:46:08.000Z","msg":"Sorry 錯post<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13a90b78dca3ed8c65fb4934d9eaaf73eefad64d","tid":2345952,"uid":20867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T04:53:38.000Z","msg":"中港之間有引渡協議<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}